⟨ PohLang Android Activity ⟩
⟨ Main entry point for Android application ⟩

Set activity_title to "PohLang App"
Set content_text to "Welcome to PohLang on Android!"

⟨ Activity Lifecycle ⟩
Define function onCreate with parameters bundle:
    Write "Activity created"
    Call setupUI
    Call loadData
End function

Define function onStart:
    Write "Activity started"
    Call connectServices
End function

Define function onResume:
    Write "Activity resumed"
    Call refreshUI
End function

Define function onPause:
    Write "Activity paused"
    Call saveState
End function

Define function onStop:
    Write "Activity stopped"
    Call disconnectServices
End function

Define function onDestroy:
    Write "Activity destroyed"
    Call cleanup
End function

⟨ UI Setup ⟩
Define function setupUI:
    Write "Setting up UI components"
    Call createToolbar with title activity_title
    Call createMainContent
    Call setupEventListeners
End function

Define function createMainContent:
    Write content_text
    Call displayWelcomeMessage
End function

⟨ Data Management ⟩
Define function loadData:
    Write "Loading application data"
    Set data_loaded to true
End function

Define function saveState:
    Write "Saving application state"
End function

⟨ Service Integration ⟩
Define function connectServices:
    Write "Connecting to backend services"
End function

Define function disconnectServices:
    Write "Disconnecting from services"
End function

⟨ UI Updates ⟩
Define function refreshUI:
    Write "Refreshing user interface"
End function

⟨ Cleanup ⟩
Define function cleanup:
    Write "Cleaning up resources"
End function

⟨ Event Handlers ⟩
Define function setupEventListeners:
    Write "Setting up event listeners"
End function

⟨ Utilities ⟩
Define function displayWelcomeMessage:
    Write "╔════════════════════════════╗"
    Write "║  PohLang Android App      ║"
    Write "║  Version 1.0.0            ║"
    Write "╚════════════════════════════╝"
End function

Define function createToolbar with parameters title:
    Write "Creating toolbar with title: " + title
End function
